snippet.textDisplay: okay so I kind of did the same for my bf this year except it almost didn't cost me anything. For the gals on a budget: buy a regular chocolate advent calendar. Then write 24 notes with cute little things to do for your significant other. E.g. massage, why you love him/her, choose dinner, choose a dessert etc. Tape the notes on the chocolate advent calendar. And you're done and almost didn't spend anything.
